/pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/veteran-truda-udostoverenie-i-dengi_0003-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Ветеран труда удостоверение деньги пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/nazvany-kriterii-polucheniya-veterana-truda-bez-nagrad-eshhe-v-neskolkih-regionah/\">Criteria for obtaining veteran labor without rewards in several regions</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">PNZ.RU has already written that in a number of regions it is not necessary to have departmental awards in order to obtain the title of &amp;quot; Labour &amp;quot; . Logs only</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rekordnaya-indeksacziya-komu-povysyat-pensii-posle-1-marta/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/pensioner_0013-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rekordnaya-indeksacziya-komu-povysyat-pensii-posle-1-marta/\">Record indexation: Who will increase pensions after 1 March</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">The index of pensions and benefits is planned annually based on forecasts of food prices, non-food items and services.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rossiyane-poluchili-vozmozhnost-uvelichit-pensiyu-na-15-000-rublej/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/pensioner_0091-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rossiyane-poluchili-vozmozhnost-uvelichit-pensiyu-na-15-000-rublej/\">Russia was able to increase the pension by 15,000 roubles</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">Since 2024, a programme of long-term savings has been launched in Russia. This tool is intended to help the Rosians build savings, and it allows</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/do-1954-goda-usloviya-polucheniya-statusa-veterana-velikoj-otechestvennoj-vojny-rasshiryayut/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/pensioner_0035-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/do-1954-goda-usloviya-polucheniya-statusa-veterana-velikoj-otechestvennoj-vojny-rasshiryayut/\">Until 1954: conditions for obtaining the status of veteran of the Great Patriotic War expand</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">In the State Duma, the Russian Federation will consider a bill to expand the category of persons who are entitled to the rank of veteran of the Great Patriotic War.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rabotayushhie-pensionery-lishayutsya-ne-tolko-indeksaczii-no-i-pensionnyh-koefficzientov/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/pensioner_0074-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rabotayushhie-pensionery-lishayutsya-ne-tolko-indeksaczii-no-i-pensionnyh-koefficzientov/\">Employed retirees are excluded not only by indexing but also by pension ratios</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">In 2024, working retirees were again left without January indexation, a moratorium still in effect. How pensions are recosted, explained</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/lgoty-invalidov-na-transporte-rasprostranyayut-na-vseh-pensionerov/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/pensionery-v-avtobus-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"пенсионеры автобус\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/lgoty-invalidov-na-transporte-rasprostranyayut-na-vseh-pensionerov/\">Persons with disabilities in transport extend to all pensioners</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">A bill amending article 21.1 of the Federal Law on Road Transport was submitted to the lower house of Parliament.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/v-marte-veteranov-pooshhryat-novoj-vyplatoj/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dengi-pyatitysyachnye-2-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Деньги пятитысячные\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/v-marte-veteranov-pooshhryat-novoj-vyplatoj/\">In March, veterans will encourage new payment</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">Another category of Russian citizens will be able to receive a payment of 50,000 roubles this year. This is an opportunity for the veterans of the Great Fatherland.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/komu-polozheny-federalnye-doplaty-za-bolshoj-stazh-v-2024-godu/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/pensioner_0050-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/komu-polozheny-federalnye-doplaty-za-bolshoj-stazh-v-2024-godu/\">To whom federal long-term bonuses are paid in 2024</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">Adjustment of service years is important not only for the maintenance of pension rights. If it turns out to be outside the statutory limits, it becomes available.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/komu-iz-pensionerov-mozhno-snizit-platu-za-zhku-v-2024-godu/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"htt